<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="switch-off">switch off</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>关上 (电灯、电视等)；[非正式用语] 不听；不理睬：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Please switch off the TV when you go to bed.
睡觉时请关上电视。</p><footer>北师大① – 1</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Thankfully, I’ve learned to switch off and let it go over my head.
谢天谢地，我已经学会了不再烦恼，把它抛到脑后。</p></div></div>